r, 52, proud in his native France.\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7071746849385204, \"rank\": 0.4114281458302621, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"both the high-dive 10m synchronised and individual disciplines\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young diver will first compete in the 10m synchronised platform final alongside fellow Brit Lois Toulson as she hopes to secure her first Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lois_Toulson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lois Toulson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lois_Toulson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lois_Toulson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The young diver\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC's Young Sports Personality of the Year for 2017 will then participate in the qualifying rounds for the individual 10m event on August 5, with potential further success in the finals if she qualifies.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9212332583232613, \"rank\": 0.072800986